<items>
<text label="T1"><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="720"/><tabStop position="1440"/><tabStop position="2160"/><tabStop position="2880"/><tabStop position="3600"/><tabStop position="4320"/><tabStop position="5040"/><tabStop position="5760"/><tabStop position="6480"/><tabStop position="7200"/><tabStop position="7920"/><tabStop position="8640"/><tabStop position="9360"/><tabStop position="10080"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000"><b>Rosters from the 4 groups of teams:</b></font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="720"/><tabStop position="1440"/><tabStop position="2160"/><tabStop position="2880"/><tabStop position="3600"/><tabStop position="4320"/><tabStop position="5040"/><tabStop position="5760"/><tabStop position="6480"/><tabStop position="7200"/><tabStop position="7920"/><tabStop position="8640"/><tabStop position="9360"/><tabStop position="10080"/></tabPositions></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="720"/><tabStop position="1440"/><tabStop position="2160"/><tabStop position="2880"/><tabStop position="3600"/><tabStop position="4320"/><tabStop position="5040"/><tabStop position="5760"/><tabStop position="6480"/><tabStop position="7200"/><tabStop position="7920"/><tabStop position="8640"/><tabStop position="9360"/><tabStop position="10080"/></tabPositions><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000">You will choose </font><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000"><b>one column,</b></font><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000"> from which you will draft your roster. You will get </font><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000"><b>one player</b></font><font face="Arial" size="200" color="000000"> from each group. Go ahead. Create more than one team. Have fun. </font></paragraph><paragraph indent="0" align="left"><tabPositions><tabStop position="720"/><tabStop position="1440"/><tabStop position="2160"/><tabStop posit